==Most prominent summits==
{{GeoGroup|section=Most prominent summits}}
{{see also|List of the ultra-prominent summits of Greenland}}
Of the most prominent summits of Greenland, only Gunnbjørn Fjeld exceeds {{convert|3000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence.  Six peaks exceed {{convert|2000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} and [[List of Ultras of Greenland|38 peaks are ultra-prominent summits with at least {{convert|1500|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence]].
{{clear}}
