==Most isolated major summits==
{{GeoGroup|section=Most isolated major summits}}
Of the most isolated major summits of Greenland, only Gunnbjørn Fjeld exceeds {{convert|3000|km|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic isolation.  Four peaks exceed {{convert|500|km|1|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic isolation, 13 peaks exceed {{convert|200|km|1|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}}, and 21 peaks exceed {{convert|100|km|2|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic isolation.
{{clear}}
